description:
ADV / web-engineering co. is a leading provider of development and systems integration services. We are Microsoft Gold Partner and Bitrix Gold Partner. We are also proficient in PHP and PHP-based frameworks and products as well as Atlassian products and mobile development technologies. 
 
Our core areas of expertise are:
e-commerce (B2B, B2C, marketplaces) – building solutions from the scratch and improving on the existing solutions, optimizing sales funnels, drastically increasing conversion, increasing loyalty and retention;
digital transformation of customer service – cutting costs while increasing convenience by deploying automated customer service and account management systems, personalizing cross-selling and upselling through intelligent customer dashboards;
intranet and internal business process solutions –maximizing organizational effectiveness and employee engagement through internal communication solutions (portals, networks, banks), gamification, workflow automation.
